Alien Breed 3d - AGA only

Controls: J - Joystick
          M - Mouse
          K - Keys (cursors + alt to file)
Shift - Run
Space + forward into door - open door
Space - operate lift
Space - flick switch

Hints:
* To get inside, you'll need to find a door.
* Aliens can hit you through doors
* To finish, find the switch - you'll need to find some keys first, though.
* Select the plasma gun with the "2" key.
* You cannot kill the walkers, so RUN AWAY!!!


